description.en:
DeepCloud AI is building an AI driven low latency decentralized cloud infrastructure for next generation of apps and IoT

We will provide a spot market for computing and storage resources for enterprise-level users and individuals, for the purpose of sharing their excess capacity on our decentralized cloud, and with our AI matching engine. Applications will execute in a secure sandbox on the peer-to-peer resources, and all transactions are managed on the blockchain via smart contracts.

We will also offer a DApps marketplace for developers with pre-validated applications to speed up the development of their end to end solutions.
